{"headings": [{"tag": "h1", "text": "Get in Touch", "rect": {"x": 424, "y": 228.98, "width": 592, "height": 46.8, "bottom": 275.78, "right": 1016, "area": 27703.75}, "styles": {"fontSize": "36px", "fontWeight": "700", "fontFamily": "Georgia, serif", "color": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLeftWidth": "0px", "borderTopLeftRadius": "0px", "borderTopRightRadius": "0px", "borderBottomLeftRadius": "0px", "borderBottomRightRadius": "0px", "paddingTop": "0px", "paddingRight": "0px", "paddingBottom": "0px", "paddingLeft": "0px", "marginTop": "0px", "marginRight": "0px", "marginBottom": "24px", "marginLeft": "0px", "textAlign": "start", "boxShadow": "none", "backgroundImage": "none"}}], "paragraphs": [{"text": "I welcome notes from readers \u2014 about books you think I should know, quiet recommendations, translations you've been working on, or simply something that struck you on a long walk. I also read every message about writing commissions, copywriting work, and editorial collaborations, though I may take a few sleepless evenings to reply.", "length": 333, "rect": {"x": 424, "y": 299.78, "width": 592, "height": 161.95, "bottom": 461.73, "right": 1016, "area": 95876.25}, "styles": {"fontSize": "18px", "fontWeight": "400", "fontFamily": "system-ui, -apple-system, \"system-ui\", \"Segoe UI\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif", "color": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "backgroundColor": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)", "display": "block", "position": "static", "borderTopColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderRightColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderBottomColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderLeftColor": "rgb(26, 26, 26)", "borderTopWidth": "0px", "borderRightWidth": "0px", "borderBottomWidth": "0px", "borderLef